The paper deals with the problem of schema refactoring in database programs, which is a core concern of database systems (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). The proposed technique involves synthesizing a new version of a program, which is a topic of interest in programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The method also involves ensuring equivalence between the original and synthesized programs, which is a key concern in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
